<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>    
    <title>Cadastro de novas linhas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/bulk.css" /> 
</head> 
<body>
<form action="/insert" method="POST"> 
    <header>
        <div id="header">
            <h1><%= title %></h1>  
            <p>Coloque os n√∫meros das linhas abaixo, separadas por espa√ßo ou quebra de linha. <b>Aten√ß√£o na hora de cadastrar üòâ!</b></p>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main> 
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                <th id="contLinhas">0</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <tr id="primeiraLinha"> 
                <td id="linhas" rowspan="501"><textarea required maxlength="5999" name="contLinhas" rows="500" cols="11" ></textarea></td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </main>
    <aside> 
        <div id="filtros">
            <a href="/"><button type="button">Voltar</button></a>
            <label><p> <span class="titulo"> Local: </span> </p><br>
                <select name="local" required>
                        <option></option>
                        <option value="Estoque_CT">Estoque CT</option>
                        <option>Virtual</option>
                        <option>-</option>
                        <option value="Estoque_BBA">Estoque BBA</option>
                        <option value="Com_colaborador">Com colaborador</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Raz√£o Social: </span> <br>
                <select name="razao" required>
                        <option></option>
                        <option>REDECARD</option>
                        <option>LUIZACRED</option>
                        <option>KINEA_PRIVATE_EQUITY</option>
                        <option>KINEA_INVESTIMENTOS</option>
                        <option>ITAUSEG_SAUDE</option>
                        <option>ITAU_VIDA_PREVIDENCIA</option>
                        <option>ITAU_UNIBANCO</option>
                        <option>ITAU_UNIBANCO_HOLDING</option>
                        <option>ITAU_SEGUROS</option>
                        <option>ITAU_CORRETORA_VALORES</option>
                        <option>ITAU_CORRETORA_SEGUROS</option>
                        <option>ICARROS_LTDA</option>
                        <option>HIPERCARD_BCO_MULTIPLO</option>
                        <option>FUNDACAO_SAUDE_ITAU</option>
                        <option>FUND_ITAU_CLUBE</option>
                        <option>FINANC_ITAU_CBD</option>
                        <option>BANCO_ITAUCARD</option>
                        <option>BANCO_ITAU_CONSIGNADO</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Plano: </span> <br>
                <select name="plano" required>
                        <option></option>
                        <option>Smart2GB</option>
                        <option>Smart5GB</option>
                        <option>Dados3GB</option>
                        <option>Dados5GB</option>
                        <option>Dados10GB</option>
                        <option>SmartVoz</option>
                        <option>BOX100GB</option>
                        <option>TORPEDO</option>
                        <option>Smart10GB</option>
                        <option>Smart25GB</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Status: </span> <br>
                <select name="status" required>
                    <option></option>
                        <option>ATIVO</option>
                        <option>DESATIVO</option>
                        <option>PERDA_ROUBO</option>
                        <option>CANCELADA</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Extra: </span> <br>
                <select name="extra" disabled>
                        <option></option>
                        <option>BloqDevolucao</option>
                        <option>BloqEstoque</option>
                        <option>MapRedDesativo</option>
                        <option>MapRedPerdaRoubo</option>
                        <option>MapRedNaoBloq</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Grupo: </span> <br>
                <input list="grupo" name="grupo">
                <datalist id="grupo">
                <% distinctGrupo.forEach(function(grupos){ %>
                    <option><%= grupos %></option>
                <% }) %>
                </datalist>
            </label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> OBS: </span> <br>
            <textarea maxlength="60" name="obs" rows="3" cols="28" placeholder="Digite uma observa√ß√£o sucinta..."></textarea></label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Motivo: </span> <br>
            <textarea maxlength="60" name="motivo" rows="3" cols="28" placeholder="Digite de forma breve o motivo da sua altera√ß√£o..."></textarea></label>
            <label><span class="titulo"> Bloqueio Gest√£o: </span> <br>
                <select name="bloqGestao" disabled>
                    <option>Desbloqueado</option>
                    <option>Bloqueado</option>
                </select>
            </label>
            <br><br>
            <input type="submit" name="insertBtn" value="Cadastrar linhas" />    
        </div>
    </aside>
</form>
    <script src="/javascript/insert.js" ></script>
</body> 
</html>